data.description: Welcome to Tama County this small town home boasts 3 bedrooms 3 bathrooms.... I really feal this house is a lot bigger than it says. With 3 bedrooms & 3 full baths along with a family room &  living room with an eat in kitchen or formal dining area. Basement has a ton of space with the Family room area for entertaining on the big screen & workout area not to mention the large non conforming bedroom & a full bath. Thaere is ample room for storage & a wood workers paradise secluded area. Many of the rooms have had a fresh coat of warm gray paint & new carpet throughout the main level. The 2 car garage is oversized for plenty of room for 2 cars & work bench. There is also a small shed in back yard for lawn mowers or lawn equipment. This home really is a great house "move in ready' schedule your showing today.
